# Workflow Graph (Architecture Overview)

## Workflow / Data Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  U[User] -->|Browse| FE[React Vite Frontend]
  FE -->|Route| R{React Router}

  R -->|Home| H[Home Page]
  R -->|Products| P[Products Page]
  R -->|Product detail| PD[ProductDetail Page]
  R -->|Search/Filters| S[SearchBar + Filters]

  P --> API1[Mock API Layer: src/services/api.ts]
  PD --> API1
  API1 --> MD[(Mock Data: src/data/mockData.ts)]

  R -->|Cart| C[Cart Page]
  C --> CartCtx[CartContext]
  CartCtx --> LS[localStorage]
  C --> API2[Mock Cart API]

  R -->|Checkout| CK[Checkout Page]
  CK --> Addr[Shipping Address Step]
  CK --> Pay[Payment Step (Mock)]
  CK --> Review[Order Review]
  Pay -->|success/failure| PAYRES[Payment result]
  CK --> API3[Mock Order API]
  API3 --> O[(Orders State)]

  U -->|Login/Register| AU[Auth Pages]
  AU --> AuthCtx[AuthContext (JWT)]
  AuthCtx --> Store[(localStorage/session)]

  R -->|Orders / Tracking| OD[Orders + OrderDetail]
  OD --> API4[Mock Order API]
  API4 --> O

  R -->|Admin| AD[Admin Page]
  AD --> API5[Admin CRUD: products/orders]
  API5 --> O
  API5 --> MD

  FE --> UI[Reusable Components (Navbar/Footer/UI library)]
```

## Major Modules
- **Frontend UI**: `src/app/App.tsx`, `src/pages/*`, `src/components/*`
- **Routing**: React Router
- **State**: `src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx`, `src/contexts/CartContext.tsx`
- **API layer**: `src/services/api.ts` (mock endpoints)
- **Data**: `src/data/mockData.ts`, types in `src/types/index.ts`

## Lifecycle Summary
1. User navigates product/catalog pages.
2. Frontend calls mock API/services.
3. User adds items to cart; cart state persists via localStorage.
4. User checks out; payment is simulated.
5. Order is created via mock order API.
6. User views orders/tracking.
7. Admin manages products/orders via admin UI.

